.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115342\/morocco-guide-saltinourhair-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115342\/morocco-guide-saltinourhair-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115342\/morocco-guide-saltinourhair-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115342\/morocco-guide-saltinourhair-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115342\/morocco-guide-saltinourhair-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115342\/morocco-guide-saltinourhair-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115342\/morocco-guide-saltinourhair-1440x960.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115342\/morocco-guide-saltinourhair-30x20.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115342\/morocco-guide-saltinourhair.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Chefchaouen is much quieter and calmer than other cities in Morocco, so you can spend hours here calmly wandering the blue alleys, and taking photos of cute porches and doorways in the sun. The blue houses of this city are easily the top thing to do in Chefchaouen!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/morocco\/marrakech-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The ultimate 3 day Marrakech guide!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Note:<\/strong> Make sure to be respectful at all times, as local people do live inside the houses. Some &#x2018;Insta famous&#x2019; doorways will charge you a small fee to take a photo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115332\/blue-streets-585x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"244\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-32121 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115332\/blue-streets-585x810.jpg 585w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115332\/blue-streets-300x416.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115332\/blue-streets-600x831.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115332\/blue-streets-433x600.jpg 433w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115332\/blue-streets-244x338.jpg 244w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115332\/blue-streets-1109x1536.jpg 1109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115332\/blue-streets-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115332\/blu