 city. Add this as one of your things to do on your Chefchaouen itinerary. Wake up in the early morning, get to the rooftop of your riad, and enjoy the most magical sunrise you will see during your trip. Alternatively, enjoy this magical moment from higher up, by enjoying one of the many hikes out of the city up into the Riff Mountains. This is highly recommended to get a fantastic view of the city!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/chefchaouen-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">See all places to stay in Chefchaouen<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115416\/best-things-to-do-chefcaouen-sunrise.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do chefchaouen sunrise\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"303\" alt=\"best things to do chefchaouen sunrise\" class=\"wp-image-32099 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115416\/best-things-to-do-chefcaouen-sunrise.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115416\/best-things-to-do-chefcaouen-sunrise-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115416\/best-things-to-do-chefcaouen-sunrise-600x404.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uplo