0.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115404\/streets-morocco-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"sunrise\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sunrise\" class=\"wp-image-32105 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-720x1080.jpg 720w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-960x1440.jpg 960w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise.jpg 1280w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-20x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/23115401\/sunrise-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>3. Visit the Spanish Mosque&#xA0;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Spanish Mosque is a beautiful building that sits isolated on a hill above Chefchaouen. The mosque was built in the 1920s, during the war. However, it was never actually used and now sits abandoned, looking out across the city. It is an easy 30-minute hike to the top, where you will be rewarded with incredible views. <\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3592&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114903\/chefchaouen-morocco-guide.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114903\/chefchaouen-morocco-guide-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23114903\/chefchaouen-morocco-guide-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"9 Best Things To Do In Chefchaouen, Morocco\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Seeing the sunset is magical here, as the golden colors hit the background of the earthy Riff mountains. However, at this time there can be crowds as it is one of the most popular things to do in Chefchaouen. If you prefer it to be quieter, take a very early morning hike to see the sunrise instead.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Also, see the <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/morocco\/morocco-route-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">10-day Morocco Route<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>4. <strong>Shopping in the Medina<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Visit the narrow blue, twisting streets of the Medina, and its souks! The souks may not be as big as in other Moroccan cities like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/morocco\/fes-morocco\/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"undefined (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Fes<\/a> but it remains a popular shopping destination. This is because it offers many native handicrafts that are not available anywhere else in Morocco, such as wool garments, woven blankets, and woven baskets. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco.jpg\" alt=\"chefchaouen blue city morocco\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"291\" alt=\"chefchaouen blue city morocco\" class=\"wp-image-32101 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-300x194.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-600x388.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-800x517.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-1080x698.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-450x291.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-1536x992.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-30x19.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-163x105.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-279x180.jpg 279w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-768x496.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-1024x661.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-1440x930.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco-30x19.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115410\/chefcaouen-blue-city-morocco.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In between the handicrafts, you&#x2019;ll often find pots of bright-colored paint powders in a variety of pastel colors, which is a beautiful scene against the backdrop of blue walls. Goats cheese is also popular with tourists and served with many dishes. Well worth a try, and a tasty thing to do in Chefchaouen.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>Throughout Morocco, bargaining is common practice. Always haggle for a price, and don&#x2019;t except the first offer.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"blue city morocco streets\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"blue city morocco streets\" class=\"wp-image-32108 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-streets-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115353\/blue-city-morocco-s