ttps:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina-720x1080.jpg 720w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina-960x1440.jpg 960w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina.jpg 1280w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina-20x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115350\/chefcaouen-shopping-medina-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>5. The Kasbah Museum<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In the main square, sits the Kasbah: an old Moroccan fort. This building has served many purposes through the ages, most notably as a prison, and now it is an ethnographic museum and art gallery. Inside there are also beautiful <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Spanish<\/a> style gardens, which provide a nice area of calm away from the city. Learn about the fascinating history of this area, through the ancient artifacts, clothing, instruments, and traditional decorations and crafts on display. The fort tower can be climbed to discover beautiful views over the city.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Entrance fee:<\/strong> 60 MAD. Note that the descriptions in the tower are not in English.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>6. Plaza Uta El-Hammam<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Many things happen around the hustle and bustle of the main square in Chefchaouen: Plaza Uta El-Hammam. Sitting in the center of the medina, the square is surrounded by restaurants, shops, the Kasbah, and the Grand Mosque. The Grand Mosque is still used for religious worship so it is not open for tourists, however, its unique octagonal minaret can be viewed from the square. Sit by the tree, in the center of the cobbled square, and people watch for a break from sightseeing &#x2013; a fun thing to do while in Chefchaouen.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/chefchaouen-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">See all places to stay in Chefchaouen<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center.jpg\" alt=\"blue city center\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"blue city center\" class=\"wp-image-32120 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-1440x960.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center-30x20.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115335\/blue-city-center.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>7. <strong>Enjoy the Nature Around Chefchaouen<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Riff mountains provide the perfect setting for beautiful nature and wildlife. We didn&#x2019;t leave the town ourselves but we&#x2019;ve heard good experiences from fellow travelers about these spots:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Ras El Maa Waterfall.<\/strong> This is a small but beautiful waterfall situated on the outskirts of the medina, amongst pretty woodland. Sit and enjoy a mint tea here, dangle your feet in the cool mountain water, and watch locals wash their clothes here.&#xA0; It can be reached via the hiking trail that takes you up to the Spanish Mosque, so it is a nice thing to do in Chefchaouen if you have time to stop while passing by.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<ol start=\"2\"><li><strong>Jeb Al Kalaa.<\/strong> This is the mountain overlooking Chefchaouen. This is an intermediate hike of about 6-8 hours. The trail can be hard to follow, so be confident in your navigation or book a guide to lead you. Once at the top, there are phenomenal panoramic views over the mountains and the blue city below. An amazing thing to do in Chefchaouen if you have a day to spare.&#xA0;<\/li><\/ol>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ol start=\"3\"><li><strong>Talassemtane National Park.<\/strong>&#x2013; less than 45 minutes&#x2019; drive from Chefchaouen is this fantastic national park, full of natural wonders. Hire a guide to take you on some memorable hikes here.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<ol start=\"4\"><li><strong>Bridge of God and Akchour Waterfalls.<\/strong> Sitting within the Talassemtane National Park is the area of Akchour, filled with stunning emerald pools, waterfalls, and canyons. Make sure to visit the Akchour waterfalls and the Bridge of God, which is an impressive natural stone arch 25 meters above the gorge. Both are reached on foot, via steep hiking trails, so prepare yourself for a bit of a walk!<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/morocco\/sahara-desert-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">For more nature, head for the Sahara Desert!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"restaurants\">8. <strong>Experience Delicious Food<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The flavor of Moroccan food is unlike anything else. On each corner of the cute streets, you will find homemade bread baked by people in their wood-fired ovens. At restaurants, they serve typical Moroccan dishes of couscous, fish, spices, and vegetables. Enjoy sitting on beautiful Morrocan cushions, in romantically lit dining rooms, eating tagine out of a locally made tagine bowl &#x2013; a truly authentic way to understand the culture of Morocco and Chefchaouen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen.jpg\" alt=\"best food chefchaouen\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"best food chefchaouen\" class=\"wp-image-32107 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115357\/best-food-chefcaouen-1024x683.jpg 1024