=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Head to Chez Aladdin, for its terrace, with stunning rooftop views over the city (located just off the main square). For lunch or dinner, we also highly recommend Restaurant Populaire Bab Ssour. Breakfast is best enjoyed in the main square!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen.jpg\" alt=\"best breakfast chefchaouen\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"334\" alt=\"best breakfast chefchaouen\" class=\"wp-image-32123 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-300x223.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-600x445.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-800x593.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-1080x801.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-450x334.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-1536x1139.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-163x121.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-243x180.jpg 243w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-768x570.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-1024x759.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-1440x1068.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen-30x22.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115327\/best-breakfast-chefcaouen.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>9. <strong>Take the Beautiful Bus Ride to Fes<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#x2019;re traveling around Morocco it&#x2019;s a good choice to take the local bus to, or from, Fes. The beautiful scenery you will see as you travel through the magical landscapes of Morocco is well worth a few hours on a bus. Better still, is the breathtaking view of Chefchaouen, as you approach the city for the first time. Take one of the CTM buses (the biggest operator in Morocco), and enjoy a comfortable ride of approximately 4 hours.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Must Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/morocco\/fes-morocco\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The best things to do in Fes<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115347\/chefcaouen-morocco-best-things-to-do.jpg\" alt=\"chefchaouen morocco best things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"330\" alt=\"chefchaouen morocco best things to do\" class=\"wp-image-32114 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115347\/chefcaouen-morocco-best-things-to-do.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115347\/chefcaouen-morocco-best-things-to-do-300x220.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115347\/chefcaouen-morocco-best-things-to-do-600x440.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115347\/chefcaouen-morocco-best-things-to-do-800x587.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115347\/chefcaouen-morocco-best-things-to-do-1080x792.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115347\/chefcaouen-morocco-best-things-to-do-450x330.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115347\/chefcaouen-morocco-best-things-to-do-1536x1126.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115347\/chefcaouen-morocco-best-things-to-do-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23115347\/chefcaouen-morocco-best-things-to-do-163x120.jpg 163w, 