erience. Most of the riads and hotels range from budget to high-level luxury. Many of the riads on the more luxurious end will also have spas to enjoy! Be aware that staying inside the medina itself can be a bit more expensive, however, there are some good hostel options here too.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Hostels Chefchaouen<\/h3>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/hostel-mauritania\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23163050\/hostel-chefchaouen-morocco-30x20.jpg\" alt=\"Hostel Mauritania\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/23163050\/hostel-chefchaouen-morocco-450x307.jpg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">Hostel Mauritania<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/airbnb-dar-chefchaoen\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113807\/6c372103_original-30x23.jpg\" alt=\"Dar Onsar\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23113807\/6c372103_original-450x338.jpg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <d